subSubSection.paragraph:
Remarks. This species is similar to
Tetra smilaxis
Xue, Song & Hong, 2006
, but can be differentiated by coxal area with granules (coxal area smooth in
T . smilaxis
), empodium 7 -rayed (empodium 4 -rayed in
T . smilaxis
), admedian and submedian lines separate (admedian and submedian lines connected in
T . smilaxis
).
